The Balrog DB    </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000">Strategy</Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">This decks strategy isnt that complicated, its about discarding.<br />
<br />
My fellowship isnt easily beaten, because of low twilight on site 4 and 5 (Gimli DotMR), and later on I have Aragorn, Sam and Thrarin as cannon fodder. And also, I can boost Frodo up to 13, and with Bounder, 39 is needed to overwhelm. But it still have some weaknesses, like if I wont get my own sites out and two fierce nazgul attacks on site 2 or 3. Or repeated swarms attacking on site 7-9, I can only hops I discard the Goblin Swarms and Armories.<br />
<br />
There isnt much to say about the shadow side. I hope i can discard and get burdens on the ring-bearer fast enough to use The Irresistible Shadow. And I want to go second to get my site 2, it sometimes discards the opponents whole hand. The Enheartened Foes are used with the Tower Lieutenants, and the Tower Assassins are used to kill unique allies and later hope to get a chance to use Orc Butchery. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
